   What's NEKOPARA? Why, it's a cat paradise!  This is  a  story  just
   before  Kashou  opened  "La Soleil".  The eldest  daughter  of  the
   Minaduki household and their 6 catgirls go to wake up their master;
   prepare breakfast; clean  up the  house; go  out on  a  walk;  make
   dinner; take a bath; sleep together; et cetera, et cetera.
